description:
This is a 50 minute workout called 'Saturday Sweat Session | 45 Min Rhythm Ride Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: We're ending this week with a good rhythm ride indoor cycling sweat session on your exercise bike! Bring two towels for this indoor cycling workout!
